#### Creating Development Dockers
```shell
cd hansroh/lib/ecsdep
docker-compose -f dep/compose.devel.yml
```

#### Testing `app` and `ecsdep`
```shell
docker attach ecsdep
cd tests && ./test-all.sh
```

#### Testing Deployment
```shell
docker attach docker

test_ecs_docker_build.sh
test_ecsdep_deploy.sh
```

#### Testing Gitlab CI/CD
```shell
git push origin master
```

.gitlab.ci
```shell
./test_ecs_docker_build.sh
./test_ecsdep_deploy.sh
```

